abstract: Islamic State gunmen and suicide bomber in bulldozer full of explosives ambush Iraqi Army convoy north of Falluja; four officers and unknown number of soldiers are killed.
lead_paragraph: Fighters from the Islamic State group ambushed an Iraqi Army convoy on Friday with a bulldozer packed with explosives.

headline.main: Iraq: ISIS Kills an Army Commander
